decodeAndRecoverDelegatedTokenSetup(byte.notice: Decode and recover delegated token setup data from a signature. Works with multiple versions of a signature.  Takes an abi encoded premint config, version of the encoded premint config, and a signature, decodes the config, and recoveres the signer of the config.  Based on the premint config, builds setup actions for the token to be created.
